entries.journal_entry_description: Now that you're on Naboo, you must find new information that will lead you to the droid technology you seek.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: According to your contact, an old war bunker near Kaadara is rumored to hold relics from the Battle of Naboo. Among them might be the droid AI you seek. It's unlikely that much will remain, but search the bunker for anything of interest.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: This is Colonel Panaka. Why are you using Sgt.Willoc's comm? I haven't heard from him in over a week. Report to me immediately, please. I'm sending my location.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: This is Colonel Panaka. Why are you using Sgt.Willoc's comm? I haven't heard from him in over a week. Report to me immediately, please. I'm sending my location.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Panaka Responds to the RSF Comm
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Report to Colonel Panaka as requested.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You need to find out what the Skaak Tippers are planning. Attack gang members on the outskirts of town. Maybe you'll find a clue about what they're doing.
entries.task04_message_box_text: You found a radio on one of the Skaak Tippers. Maybe you should activate it and listen in?
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Activate the Skaak Tipper radio and listen.
entries.task07_comm_message_text: ...just go. Okay, fine. Here are the coordinates again. Just hurry. We have to get these weapons out of sight quickly.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Skaak Tippers are smuggling in weapons. This cannot be good. Go to the location where the weapons are being smuggled in and recover as many crates as you can.
entries.task08_journal_entry_title: Defeat Skaak Tippers and Confiscate the Weapon Crates
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Return to Colonel Panaka and let him know what you've learned.
